-- Embraer to Meet 2010 Forecasts, Expects `Slow' 2011 Business, Chief Says
-- B y   F a b i o l a   M o u r a
-- 2010-12-14T15:22:10Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-14/embraer-to-meet-2010-forecasts-expects-slow-2011-business-chief-says.html
Embraer SA will meet its 2010
revenue and margin forecasts, Chief Executive Officer Frederico
Curado told reporters in Sao Paulo today.  The Brazilian planemaker expects 2011 to be a year of
“slow recovery,” Curado said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
